markets.title: Will Trump say Vladimir/Putin at his speech at CPAC?
markets.rules_primary: If President Trump says Vladimir/Putin as part of his speech at CPAC, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: Video of his speech at CPAC will be primarily used to resolve the market; if a consensus by Kalshi employees cannot be reached using video, transcripts of his speech at CPAC will be used according to the news publications listed in the contract. The exact phrase/word, or a plural or possessive form of the phrase/word, must be used. Grammatical/tense inflections are otherwise not included. Hyphenated or compound words used with <word> will not be included.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
